{"tid":745732,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[全能到仆街]「山神」增強為熱帶風暴 天文台發酷熱天氣警告","createTime":"2018-07-17T04:52:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T05:59:39.000Z","uid":122,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"996ff76b9e98ea6a5fdfe8599ff3c61ce19f4074","tid":745732,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T04:52:02.000Z","msg":"【12:10】天文台發出酷熱天氣警告<br />\n【12:00】現時氣溫33&deg;C，相對濕度62％<br />\n【11:45】天文台表示，山神會在黃昏至晚上最接近香港<br />\n【10:45】山神已增強為一熱帶風暴<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n位於南海東北部的熱帶低氣壓今早命名為山神，並增強為一熱帶風暴。天文台會在下午稍後考慮是否發出三號強風信號。<br />\n<br />\n按照現時預測路徑，山神會在黃昏至晚上最接近香港，在本港以南約300公里掠過，預計屆時本地風力會有所增強。<br />\n<br />\n在正午12時，熱帶風暴山神集結在香港之東南約410公里，即在北緯19.3度，東經116.5度附近，預料向西移動，時速約40公里，橫過南海北部，移向海南島至雷州半島一帶。<br />\n<br />\n本港地區今日天氣預測大致多雲，短暫時間有陽光，稍後有幾陣驟雨。最高氣溫約31度。吹和緩至清勁偏東風，稍後風勢逐漸增強。海有湧浪。<br />\n<br />\n展望明日有驟雨，稍後風勢緩和。隨後一兩日短暫時間有陽光，亦有幾陣驟雨。"},{"pid":"456b4607d21fbc0190253fe454f22928e6d67001","tid":745732,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T04:52:54.000Z","msg":"抽撚夠水未？"},{"pid":"62de182b09fbed30c8660de8598217db8eb3ca6d","tid":745732,"uid":135890,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T04:55:22.000Z","msg":"全能型颱風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ab689a6a1ed1f502d2bdfe4e1f2d1afe9083ab6","tid":745732,"uid":136430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T04:55:31.000Z","msg":"全能到仆街喎"},{"pid":"ab9482f8875630b7b6451e737f96f2ffbd317de1","tid":745732,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T05:00:16.000Z","msg":"全能定仆街<br />\n又神魔同體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e69368256120559869b662b6e5a3cf960c740459","tid":745732,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T05:01:18.000Z","msg":"魔性颱風"},{"pid":"89b85e952eb46865a8c360d8b28b2a6fc4bc0472","tid":745732,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T05:01:41.000Z","msg":"廢物<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"add77caf04daa3ec2f479525504fb3376b0a7601","tid":745732,"uid":33878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T05:56:44.000Z","msg":"咁近都咁廢"},{"pid":"7ff6fd50105aeb7c85c1577a0d0d11b66ee2f922","tid":745732,"uid":51720,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T05:59:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>全能型颱風<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n🚄 特急「颱風」💨"}]}